    "The structural characteristics of the clusters can be easily understood from the silhouette values of the clusters.",
    "The silhouette values of each cluster are greater than 0.7, which indicates that these clusters are compelling for this study.In order to examine the historical growth patterns of clusters over time, a combined timeline network visualisation of keyword clusters was implemented, as shown in Fig. 11.",
